1052
01:12:16.683 --> 01:12:17.849
You never stand up for me!

1053
01:12:18.599 --> 01:12:19.974
- Be seated.
- Come with me.

1054
01:12:21.891 --> 01:12:23.266
Council continues.

1055
01:12:26.308 --> 01:12:28.349
