1058
01:12:33.683 --> 01:12:35.682
With Spider here. we're trying
to keep a low profile.

1059
01:12:35.683 --> 01:12:37.307
But that rogue is out there.

1060
01:12:37.308 --> 01:12:38.807
He's stirring up
the young bulls.

1061
01:12:38.808 --> 01:12:40.599
