would still be...

1069
01:12:59.599 --> 01:13:01.348
That wasn't my fault.

1070
01:13:01.349 --> 01:13:02.349
Dad. that...

1071
01:13:04.641 --> 01:13:05.432
That's not

1072
01:13:05.433 --> 01:13:06.433
